563
00:43:16,760 --> 00:43:18,304
-One.
-It won't take long.

564
00:43:18,387 --> 00:43:20,556
-Two.
-Just one minute will do.

565
00:43:20,639 --> 00:43:22,891
I told you to run as fast as you can.

