607
00:49:36,223 --> 00:49:40,519
As an intern, I'm forced
to work late shifts just like you.

608
00:49:40,602 --> 00:49:42,562
God, this is so exhausting.

609
00:49:42,646 --> 00:49:45,107
You can go out and have some coffee.

610
00:49:47,025 --> 00:49:48,110
Actually,

611
00:49:49,194 --> 00:49:51,655
