720
01:01:17,924 --> 01:01:21,386
During the investigation,
Park admitted to murdering Nam

721
01:01:21,469 --> 01:01:23,930
as well as to the kidnapping, confining,

722
01:01:24,013 --> 01:01:26,849
and attempted murder of Baek.

723
01:01:27,475 --> 01:01:30,728
Park claimed to have planned his crime
after harboring a grudge

724
01:01:30,812 --> 01:01:34,315
against the result
of the Yeonju Serial Murder Case.

725
01:01:36,984 --> 01:01:39,278
He is still demanding a reinvestigation.

726
01:01:39,362 --> 01:01:41,447
Meanwhile,
the Yeonju Serial Murder Case is…

727
01:02:01,092 --> 01:02:05,388
First, we'd like to thank you
for mustering up the courage to do this.

728
01:02:07,014 --> 01:02:08,766
This is all because of you.

729
01:02:11,769 --> 01:02:12,603
Pardon?

730
01:02:13,604 --> 01:02:16,190
I've been just fine
leaving all that behind.

731
01:02:18,234 --> 01:02:19,777
But after meeting you,

732
01:02:21,320 --> 01:02:23,239
her face keeps popping up in my dreams.

733
01:02:24,615 --> 01:02:25,783
Whose face?

734
01:02:27,910 --> 01:02:29,412
Ms. Jung Mi-suk's.

735
01:02:31,622 --> 01:02:33,791
She gazed at me so desperately.

736
01:02:36,335 --> 01:02:37,295
I guess

737
01:02:38,629 --> 01:02:40,423
she wants me to talk to you.

738
01:02:41,758 --> 01:02:46,512
I'll make sure
you won't regret coming here.

739
01:02:47,972 --> 01:02:51,601
All right, then. Let's go back to 2002.

740
01:02:52,727 --> 01:02:53,978
You witnessed

741
01:02:54,771 --> 01:02:56,314
Jung Mi-suk,

742
01:02:56,397 --> 01:02:59,650
Do Min-seok's last victim,
getting kidnapped,

743
01:03:00,443 --> 01:03:02,028
and reported it to the police.

744
01:03:03,488 --> 01:03:06,908
But later on, you recanted your testimony.

745
01:03:08,534 --> 01:03:09,410
Why?

746
01:03:29,347 --> 01:03:32,183
Can you tell me what this is?

747
01:03:33,643 --> 01:03:34,769
Back then,

748
01:03:35,686 --> 01:03:37,939
I had an answering machine at home.

749
01:03:39,649 --> 01:03:40,900
This is the recording.

750
01:03:47,448 --> 01:03:49,075
Dad!

751
01:03:49,158 --> 01:03:50,284
Eun-ha.

752
01:03:52,328 --> 01:03:53,579
Goodness.

753
01:03:54,288 --> 01:03:56,499
-Did you have fun today?
-Yes.

754
01:03:56,582 --> 01:03:59,252
Good girl. Let's go.

755
01:04:03,339 --> 01:04:06,050
-Dad, look at that cloud.
