such a heinous criminal is at large

784
01:06:16,847 --> 01:06:18,265
gives me goosebumps.

785
01:06:19,725 --> 01:06:21,644
No one witnessed it.

786
01:06:22,895 --> 01:06:23,771
Pardon?

787
01:06:23,854 --> 01:06:26,023
I looked into the case record,

788
01:06:26,649 --> 01:06:32,238
and no one had witnessed Do Hyeon-su
actually committing such a heinous crime.

789
01:06:34,031 --> 01:06:38,035
My husband told me
that he was different from normal people.

790
01:06:38,619 --> 01:06:42,498
That he was capable of anything, and
that's why my husband was afraid of him.

791
01:06:45,418 --> 01:06:47,086
Psychopaths

792
01:06:47,837 --> 01:06:51,382
aren't capable of taking care
of beings that are weaker than them.

793
01:06:52,550 --> 01:06:55,344
However, Do Hyeon-su
raised a dog for around ten years

794
01:06:55,886 --> 01:06:57,930
and even the puppies.

795
01:06:59,515 --> 01:07:00,725
That's a fact.

796
01:07:00,808 --> 01:07:03,060
He's on the run
after he murdered a person.

797
01:07:03,144 --> 01:07:05,646
He's a murderer. That's true.

798
01:07:06,230 --> 01:07:09,108
You're right. That's also a fact.

799
01:07:10,818 --> 01:07:13,112
But I want to uncover more.

800
01:07:13,904 --> 01:07:16,991
One should only suffer
as much as one deserves,

801
01:07:18,617 --> 01:07:20,536
whether it be legally…

802
01:07:22,329 --> 01:07:24,123
or emotionally.

803
01:07:27,334 --> 01:07:29,837
That's why I must know more.

804
01:07:31,172 --> 01:07:32,423
I want…

805
01:07:35,009 --> 01:07:36,677
to give him the punishment he deserves.

806
01:07:37,303 --> 01:07:40,014
If you read about the things
he's done on the Internet--

807
01:07:40,097 --> 01:07:41,932
This is my principle as a detective.

808
01:07:43,309 --> 01:07:44,393
I…

809
01:07:45,603 --> 01:07:47,855
only believe in what I see.

810
01:08:25,017 --> 01:08:28,062
Do Hyeon-su lived as Baek Hee-seong
for at least 14 years.

811
01:08:28,145 --> 01:08:31,023
And Baek Hee-seong's parents
have actively cooperated.

812
01:08:31,107 --> 01:08:34,735
How do you think things would've
panned out if the police considered

813
01:08:34,819 --> 01:08:38,572
the possibility that Do Min-seok
and his son might be accomplices

814
01:08:38,656 --> 01:08:40,282
during the kidnapping of Jung Mi-suk?

815
01:08:40,366 --> 01:08:42,701
You must trust me.

816
01:08:42,785 --> 01:08:46,080
This is all because
you broke your promise.

817
01:08:46,163 --> 01:08:48,707
How am I supposed to trust you now?

818
01:08:49,542 --> 01:08:52,503
I'm going to catch Do Hyeon-su.

819
01:08:54,964 --> 01:09:00,010
